He (Dr.K P Kosygan)is given instructions to take scan to the other doctors., at the time of scanning he personally seen the monitor inch by inch ...Great..(before going to the clinic prayed to my God Jesus at that time I have seen my god in all the three doctors)

I met the Dr with knee dislocation problem in Nov 2016. I had multiple ligument tear, full tear of mpfl, partial tear of acl etc. He was very kind, listened to all my problems and was very optimistic. He said surgery might not be required and giving time by getting pop for 4 weeks should heal it. I was on POP for 4 weeks and now am back to normal activities without any problem. I am very happy to be back to normal without surgery. Thanks Dr.
